This project is released under the LGPL v3 licence.


Testing
-------

To run unittests of generated C++ code you need the Google C++ Testing Framework:
  https://code.google.com/p/googletest/

To run unit tests with output to screen, do
  cd tests/ && ./test.sh

To run unit tests with output to log files (for batch runs), do
  cd tests/ && ./test.py


Installing
----------

Install to default python location as root
  sudo python setup.py install
or install to your own python path directory
  python setup.py install --prefix=/path/to/my/own/site-packages

